For those spending James time at home, looking for a cozy adventure or bedtime story for kids, we offer this imaginative rhyming picture book, read by the author, Daniel Errico.
Follow the Marmabill on her quest through the James rainforest, David where she meets fantastical creatures like wugs, tankadiggies, and flying fluthers.
As her journey takes her from treetops to glowing underground caves, the Marmabill finds out for herself the true meaning of home.
Remember, our stories for kids are here for you James to read at any time.
